column5: I just noticed it's on tonight (Discovery Channel at 10) and as I know the show has a few fans here so I figured I'd give a heads up. Filmed in "America", it would be cool if it were on Musky. I don't want to get anyones hopes up though, any fish could be the focus, it could even be an old one fimed in South America.
They had a marathon on discovery today,last one from 7-8 tonight.
So the one from 10 to 11 is a repeat? Any Musky?
Didn't watch many,no musky from what I saw. Most repeats,your right.The one at ten does not give any info.
I'm thinking its only a matter of time till Mr. Wade is fishing for Muskie on the St.Lawrence...
He's hunting fresh water monster bull shark now.
I enjoy the show and really enjoy fishing for musky myself, but compared to just about every fish he has gone after muskys are pussy cats.
Season 4 has been on for about few weeks now.  Next Episode: 9. Killer Weapons Scheduled to Air: 22 May 2012
